                    </div>
                </div><br /><br />
                <span style="font-weight:400;font-size:22px;color:black;">This is computer generated report. No signature required. Please note that the actual payment may differ from the above amount due to VAT &amp; income Tax deduction at sources where applicable. Also the amount mentioned above may vary which is subject to further checking by accounts payable of bKash.</span>
